statements: SELECT * FROM charging_stations;
SELECT station_id, location, power_output FROM charging_stations WHERE plug_type = 'Type A';
SELECT location, station_id FROM charging_stations ORDER BY last_used DESC;
SELECT AVG(power_output) AS avg_power_output FROM charging_stations;
SELECT * FROM charging_stations WHERE power_output > 10 ORDER BY location ASC;
SELECT * FROM charging_stations ORDER BY location DESC, last_used ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT station_id, location, power_output FROM charging_stations WHERE plug_type = 'Type-2' ORDER BY power_output DESC;
SELECT station_id, location FROM charging_stations WHERE last_used > '2022-09-01' ORDER BY last_used ASC;
SELECT * FROM charging_stations WHERE power_output >= 50 ORDER BY station_id LIMIT 5;
SELECT MAX(power_output) AS max_power_output, MIN(power_output) AS min_power_output FROM charging_stations;
SELECT * FROM Charging_Stations;
SELECT location, total_chargers FROM Charging_Stations WHERE total_chargers > 5;
SELECT station_id, location, total_chargers FROM Charging_Stations WHERE operational = TRUE ORDER BY location ASC;
SELECT * FROM Charging_Usage WHERE energy_consumed > 50.00 AND start_time BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-03-31';
SELECT station_id, user_id, start_time, end_time FROM Charging_Usage WHERE user_id = 100 ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT station_id, location, total_chargers, operational FROM Charging_Stations;
SELECT * FROM Charging_Usage WHERE energy_consumed > 50;
SELECT station_id, AVG(energy_consumed) AS avg_energy_consumed FROM Charging_Usage GROUP BY station_id;
SELECT * FROM Charging_Stations ORDER BY total_chargers DESC, location ASC;
SELECT station_id, location, COUNT(*) AS total_usage FROM Charging_Usage GROUP BY station_id, location HAVING COUNT(*) > 10;
SELECT * FROM charging_stations;
SELECT location, station_type FROM charging_stations WHERE num_of_ports > 2;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_info ORDER BY year DESC;

SELECT station_id, location, num_of_ports FROM charging_stations ORDER BY num_of_ports DESC;
SELECT * FROM charging_stations WHERE station_type = 'fast';
SELECT location, num_of_ports FROM charging_stations ORDER BY num_of_ports DESC;
SELECT station_id, location, last_used FROM charging_stations WHERE last_used BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT make, model, year, owner_id FROM vehicle_info WHERE year > 2015 ORDER BY year DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT vehicle_id, start_time, end_time, charged_energy FROM charging_sessions ORDER BY start_time ASC, charged_energy DESC;
SELECT * FROM charging_stations;
SELECT station_name, location FROM charging_stations WHERE usage_status = TRUE;
SELECT * FROM vehicles WHERE vehicle_type = 'Electric';
SELECT station_name, location, usage_status FROM charging_stations ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT log_id, charging_date, energy_consumed FROM charging_logs WHERE energy_consumed > 50;

SELECT station_name, location, usage_status FROM charging_stations WHERE location='Downtown';
SELECT vehicles.vehicle_id, vehicles.vehicle_type, charging_logs.charging_date FROM vehicles JOIN charging_logs ON vehicles.vehicle_id = charging_logs.vehicle_id;

SELECT charging_stations.station_name, charging_logs.energy_consumed FROM charging_stations JOIN charging_logs ON charging_stations.id = charging_logs.station_id WHERE charging_logs.energy_consumed > 50;

SELECT station_name, location FROM charging_stations UNION SELECT owner_name AS station_name, vehicle_model AS location FROM vehicles JOIN charging_logs ON vehicles.vehicle_id = charging_logs.vehicle_id WHERE charging_logs.energy_consumed < 30;
SELECT * FROM charging_stations;
SELECT station_name, location FROM charging_stations ORDER BY location ASC;

SELECT station_id, status, timestamp FROM stations_logs ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
